'''湯瑪士·威廉·謝立克'''（{{lang-en|Thomas William Selleck}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|s|ɛ|l|ɪ|k}}，{{bd|1945年|1月29日|||catIdx=Selleck}}）<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.detroitathletic.com/blog/2014/03/13/love-detroit-tigers-always-found-way-tom-sellecks-work-hollywood/ | website = Detroit Athletic | access-date = 2019-03-30 | title = His love of the Detroit Tigers has often found its way into Tom Selleck's work in Hollywood | date = 2014-03-13 | archive-date = 2019-03-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330045149/https://www.detroitathletic.com/blog/2014/03/13/love-detroit-tigers-always-found-way-tom-sellecks-work-hollywood/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>是一名美國男演員和製片人。他最著名的角色是電視劇《[[夏威夷神探|夏威夷神探]]》（1980年至1988年）中主演的{{le|湯瑪士·馬格農|Thomas Magnum}}。自2010年以來，謝立克在《[[警網急先鋒|警網急先鋒]]》中主演紐約市警察局長{{le|警網急先鋒角色列表|List of Blue Bloods characters#Frank Reagan|法蘭克·雷根}}。從2005年開始，他還在[[羅伯·派克|羅伯·派克]]小說改編的多部電視電影中飾演{{le|傑西·史東 (角色)|Jesse Stone (character)|傑西·史東}}。

在電影圈，謝立克的著名作品如《{{le|三個奶爸一個娃|Three Men and a Baby}}》（1987年）及其續集《{{le|三個奶爸一個妞|Three Men and a Little Lady}}》（1990年），還有《{{le|御準神偷|Lassiter (film)}}》（1984年）、《{{le|捍衛遊俠|Quigley Down Under}}》（1990年）和《{{le|棒球先生|Mr. Baseball}}》（1990年）。

謝立克還是{{le|加州陸軍國民警衛隊|California Army National Guard}}的資深成員、[[美国全国步枪协会|美国全国步枪协会]]的發言人、《[[國家評論|國家評論]]》雜誌廣告的代言人以及{{lang|en|Character Counts!}}組織的共同創始人。

== 早期生活 ==
=== 家庭 ===
湯姆·謝立克出生於[[密西根州|密西根州]][[底特律|底特律]]，是家庭主婦瑪莎·謝立克（{{lang|en|Martha Selleck}}，娘家姓賈格爾<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-1425048_ITM | title = Tom Selleck Plays 'Ike' In WW II Movie; Springfield Sings of the Pain of Love; Extreme Home Makeovers For Deserving Families, CNN | publisher = Accessmylibrary.com | date = 2004-05-19 | access-date = 2010-08-10 |dead-url=yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090412192322/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-1425048_ITM | archive-date = 2009-04-12}}</ref>；1921年至2017年<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/176901128/martha-jean-selleck | title = Martha Jean Jagger Selleck (1921-2017) - Find A... | website = www.findagrave.com | access-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210520085234/https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/176901128/martha-jean-selleck | dead-url = no }}</ref>）和房地產投資者兼行政人員<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.filmreference.com/film/86/Tom-Selleck.html | title = Tom Selleck Biography (1945–) | publisher = Filmreference.com | access-date = 2010-08-10 | archive-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210520085233/http://www.filmreference.com/film/86/Tom-Selleck.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2001/03/26/news/obits.html | title = California businessman, father of 'Magnum P.I.' star dies at 79 | publisher = Archives.starbulletin.com | date = 2001-03-26 | access-date = 2010-08-10 | archive-date = 2012-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120103152224/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2001/03/26/news/obits.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=uN4jAQAAIAAJ&q=%22George+Samuel+and+Nellie+Louise+(Fife)+S.;+m.+Martha+Jagger.+%22 | title = Who's who in California – Alice Catt Armstrong – Google Books | access-date = 2013-08-15 | last1 = Armstrong | first1 = Alice Catt | year = 1994 | archive-date = 2021-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210527220139/https://books.google.com/books?id=uN4jAQAAIAAJ&q=%22George+Samuel+and+Nellie+Louise+(Fife)+S.;+m.+Martha+Jagger.+%22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>羅伯特·迪安·謝立克（{{lang|en|Robert Dean Selleck}}，1921年至2001年<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/168735308/robert-dean-selleck | title = Robert Dean "Bob" Selleck, Sr (1921-2001) - Find... | website = www.findagrave.com | access-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210520085239/https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/168735308/robert-dean-selleck | dead-url = no }}</ref>）的兒子。他有一個哥哥羅伯特（{{lang|en|Robertk}}，出生於1944年）、一個妹妹瑪莎（{{lang|en|Martha}}，生於1954年）和一個弟弟丹尼爾（{{lang|en|Daniel}}，生於1950年）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-04-23-me-11551-story.html|title='What higher honor can be conferred on a woman than to be a mother, and an American mother!' --Dr. Norman Vincent Peale : Mrs. Selleck's Absent Son Steals Supermom Thunder|first1=PATRICIA WARD BIEDERMAN|last1=April 23|first2=1985 12 Am|last2=Pt|date=1985-04-23|website=Los Angeles Times|access-date=2021-05-20|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703063319/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-04-23-me-11551-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他的父親主要是英國血統，但也有遠古的德國血統，而他的母親是英國血統。透過完全父系的關係，謝立克是英國殖民者大衛·謝立克（{{lang|en|David Selleck}}）的直接後裔，他於1633年從英格蘭薩默塞特移居到馬薩諸塞州。謝立克是他的家人在北美出生的第11代。<ref>The Tom Selleck Handbook - Everything You Need to Know about Tom Selleck by Emily Smith, pg. 3</ref><ref>Tom Selleck: An Unauthorized Biography by Jason Bonderoff; New American Library, 1983. Pg. 4-5</ref>

謝立克的家人於1948年移居到加利福尼亞州{{le|舍曼奧克斯 (洛杉磯)|Sherman Oaks, Los Angeles|舍曼奧克斯}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/amp/news/martha-selleck-dead-tom-selleck-mother-was-96-982051|title=Martha Selleck Dead: Tom Selleck Mother Was 96|date=2017-03-01|website=www.hollywoodreporter.com|access-date=2021-05-20|archive-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030020020/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/amp/news/martha-selleck-dead-tom-selleck-mother-was-96-982051|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 教育 ===
謝立克1962年畢業於{{le|葛蘭特高中 (洛杉磯)|Grant High School (Los Angeles)|葛蘭特高中}}<ref>{{cite web | url = https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019593/bio | title = retrieved 2007-07-30 | publisher = Movies.yahoo.com | access-date = 2013-12-27 |dead-url=yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120117115926/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019593/bio | archive-date = 2012-01-17}}</ref>，之後就讀{{le|洛杉磯谷學院|Los Angeles Valley College}}，住在家裡並存錢<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://army.togetherweserved.com/army/servlet/tws.webapp.WebApps?cmd=ShadowBoxProfile&type=Person&ID=340877 | title = Selleck, Tom, SGT | website = Togetherweserved.com | access-date = 2019-04-06 | archive-date = 2021-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210520085450/https://army.togetherweserved.com/army/servlet/tws.webapp.WebApps?cmd=ShadowBoxProfile&type=Person&ID=340877 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大三時，他在籃球獎學金的幫助下轉到[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]，並效力於{{le|南加州大學特洛伊人男子籃球|USC Trojans men's basketball|特洛伊男子籃球}}隊<ref>{{cite web | last = Vitale | first = Dick | url = http://assets.espn.go.com/dickvitale/vcolumn010831NewYorkplusJWill.html | title = Jason Williams' injury a big topic at U.S. Open | publisher = ESPN | date = 2003-04-17 | access-date = 2010-08-10 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102346/http://assets.espn.go.com/dickvitale/vcolumn010831NewYorkplusJWill.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他是{{le|西格瑪志聯誼會|Sigma Chi|西格瑪志}}兄弟會和{{le|特洛伊騎士|Trojan Knights}}成員。在謝立克攻讀[[工商管理|工商管理]]專業時，一名戲劇教練建議他嘗試表演，並在他高三的時輟學<ref>{{Cite journal | date = 1985 | title = Tom Selleck | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_ladies-home-journal_1985-04_102_4/page/n224 | journal = The Ladies' Home Journal | volume = 102 | pages = 196 }}</ref>。隨後到{{le|麥爾頓·卡特賽拉斯|Milton Katselas}}的{{le|比佛利山劇院|Beverly Hills Playhouse}}學習表演。

=== 加州國民警衛隊 ===
[[越南戰爭|越南戰爭]]期間收到通知後，謝立克加入了{{le|加州陸軍國民警衛隊|California Army National Guard}}<ref name="military">{{cite web | title = Famous Veteran: Tom Selleck | url = http://www.military.com/veteran-jobs/career-advice/military-transition/famous-veteran-tom-selleck.html | website = military.com | publisher = Military Advantage | access-date = 2017-11-03 | archive-date = 2021-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211212191716/https://www.military.com/veteran-jobs/career-advice/military-transition/famous-veteran-tom-selleck.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1967年至1973年，他在{{le|第160步兵團 (美國)|160th Infantry Regiment (United States)|第160步兵第1營}}服役<ref name="VVMF">{{cite web | url = http://www.vvmf.org/index.cfm?SectionID=745 | title = Tom Selleck Joins Memorial Fund as the National Spokesman for the Education Center at the Wall | publisher = Vietnam Veterans Memorial Fund | date = 2009-01-28 | access-date = 2009-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824174604/http://www.vvmf.org/index.cfm?SectionID=745 |archive-date=2017-08-24 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

